## Calibration check (use when AI-drafted copy lands flat)

If you read AI-drafted copy and it sounds wrong:

1. Is it too eager? Add hedging.
2. Is it too abstract? Replace one sentence with a concrete example.
3. Is it pitching? Rewrite as observation.
4. Is it longer than three short paragraphs? Cut to half.
5. Does it use any avoid-list words? Remove.

After calibration, if a particular sample lands well, **add it to the reference samples section** above so future drafts can pattern-match.
